{"tid":2463063,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"疑就藝人與國際品牌割席抽水 IKEA專頁指「唔准跪低」","createTime":"2021-03-26T12:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:50:50.000Z","uid":212249,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f052a3349b4e171c537105181b900a738bca4431","tid":2463063,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210326/_2021032609264039889.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210326%2F_2021032609264039889.jpg&h=9a2d2c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瑞典服裝品牌H&amp;M集團與新疆棉花的「割席」風波，燃燒至adidas及Nike等國際品牌，令大批中國民眾不滿，亦有多名明星代言人紛紛發表抵制言論，與名牌「割席」。風頭火勢之際，同是源自瑞典的大型家品集團IKEA宜家家居昨晚就疑似出po「抽水」，叫人「唔准跪低」，引起網民熱烈討論！<br />\n<br />\nIKEA昨晚在Facebook專頁上發文，宣傳其鞋抽產品的減價優惠，並寫道：「我唔准你跪低⋯著鞋呀！」、「等我提你企！直！啲！」、「做人呢⋯千祈咪卑躬屈膝！」等，而網民就從字裡行間聞到陣陣「抽水味」，認為跟近日藝人與國際品牌「割席」的事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n帖文引起網民一片嘩然，不少人都指擔心小編會公司被警告，「小編會唔會收warning/被人炒」、「你小心聽日你老細局著要畀信封你」、「你今日last day？」、「唔知小編聽日仲有冇工返」，亦有不少人留言問IKEA產品用的棉花產地，疑似「反抽水」。"},{"pid":"4be17b6500ba0627f3d65c08e8f5cc32a2fbc4dc","tid":2463063,"uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:03:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2031792/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-Kelly-Online-%E7%96%91%E5%B0%B1%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E8%88%87%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%E5%89%B2%E5%B8%AD%E6%8A%BD%E6%B0%B4-IKEA%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E6%8C%87-%E5%94%94%E5%87%86%E8%B7%AA%E4%BD%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2031792%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-Kelly-Online-%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25E5%2589%25B2%25E5%25B8%25AD%25